# About 

Currated list of useful Qlik expressions and script snippets.

Source can be found in [GitHub](https://github.com/countnazgul/qlik-snippets)

# Contribute
If you want to contribute please send an email to **admin@qlik-snippets.com** with the code and short description.

**qvw/qvf** example is nice to have but not mandatory.
